{TEXT -1 5 "     " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 255 "     This works jus
t like we expect substitution to work because p2 is an operation on wh
atever is in the (  ).  However since p1 is a symbolic expression we h
ave some difficulties with substituting into it directly.   Try the fo
llowing command sequences." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG 
